      • getNumberFormatAt

        java.lang.String getNumberFormatAt(short fmtId)
        Get number format string given its id(获取给定ID的数字格式字符串)
        Parameters:
        fmtId - number format id(fmtId -数字格式id)
        Returns:
        number format code(数字格式代码)

      • putNumberFormat

        int putNumberFormat(java.lang.String fmt)
        Puts fmt in the numberFormats map if the format is not already in the the number format style table. Does nothing if fmt is already in number format style table.(如果格式尚未出现在数字格式样式表中，则将fdt放入numberbitrics的地图中。如果fdt已在数字格式样式表中，则不执行任何操作。)
        Parameters:
        fmt - the number format to add to number format style table(fdt-要添加到数字格式样式表的数字格式)
        Returns:
        the index of fmt in the number format style table(数字格式样式表中fMT的索引)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if adding the number format to the styles table would exceed the max allowed.(java.lang. IllegalStateResponse-如果将数字格式添加到样式表将超过允许的最大值。)

      • putNumberFormat

        void putNumberFormat(short index,
                     java.lang.String fmt)
        Add a number format with a specific ID into the numberFormats map. If a format with the same ID already exists, overwrite the format code with fmt This may be used to override built-in number formats.(将具有特定ID的数字格式添加到数字格式的地图中。如果已存在具有相同ID的格式，请使用fdt覆盖格式代码这可用于覆盖内置数字格式。)
        Parameters:
        index - the number format ID(index -数字格式ID)
        fmt - the number format code(fdt-数字格式代码)

      • removeNumberFormat

        boolean removeNumberFormat(short index)
        Remove a number format from the style table if it exists. All cell styles with this number format will be modified to use the default number format.(从样式表中删除数字格式（如果存在）。具有此数字格式的所有单元格样式都将被修改为使用默认数字格式。)
        Parameters:
        index - the number format id to remove(index -要删除的数字格式ID)
        Returns:
        true if the number format was removed(如果数字格式已删除，则为真)

      • removeNumberFormat

        boolean removeNumberFormat(java.lang.String fmt)
        Remove a number format from the style table if it exists All cell styles with this number format will be modified to use the default number format(从样式表中删除数字格式（如果存在）具有此数字格式的所有单元格样式都将被修改为使用默认数字格式)
        Parameters:
        fmt - the number format to remove(fdt-要删除的数字格式)
        Returns:
        true if the number format was removed(如果数字格式已删除，则为真)

      • getFontAt

        XSSFFont getFontAt(int idx)

      • putFont

        int putFont(XSSFFont font,
            boolean forceRegistration)
        Records the given font in the font table. Will re-use an existing font index if this font matches another, EXCEPT if forced registration is requested. This allows people to create several fonts then customise them later. Note - End Users probably want to call XSSFFont.registerTo(StylesTable)(在字体表中记录给定的字体。如果现有字体索引与另一种字体匹配，则将重新使用该字体索引，除非请求强制注册。这允许人们创建多种字体，然后稍后自定义它们。注意-最终用户可能想调用XSSFFont.registerTo（StylesTable）)

      • putFont
